    "body": "#2367 \r\n\r\n## Bugs to fix\r\n\r\nBug 1: `uneven_kv_smem offset` in non-TMA paged path.\r\n  - flash_fwd_sm100.py line 260: The 3-stage kv_stage upgrade (kv_stage = 3) was gated on self.use_tma_KV, so the non-TMA paged path stays at kv_stage=2 and avoids the uneven_kv_smem offset logic that cp.async can't handle due to alignment constraints.\r\n  - Affects: page_size != 128, seq_len > 128.\r\n\r\n  Bug 2: q_stage=1 kernel bug for paged non-TMA DeepSeek shape.\r\n  - `interface.py` line ~497-503: When max_seqlen_q <= tile_m (128 ≤ 128), the interface sets q_stage=1, which compiles a different kernel that produces garbage for paged non-TMA with head_dim != head_dim_v.\r\n  - Fix: force q_stage=2 when paged_kv_non_tma and `head_dim != head_dim_v`.\r\n  - Affects: any decode or short-prefill (≤128 tokens) with paged KV on DeepSeek MLA shape.\r\n\r\n## test script\r\n\r\n```python\r\n\"\"\"\r\nMinimal reproducer: flash_attn_varlen_func paged KV produces wrong results\r\nfor DeepSeek MLA shape (head_dim=192, head_dim_v=128) on SM100 (Blackwell).\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nimport torch\r\nfrom flash_attn.cute import flash_attn_varlen_func\r\n\r\n\r\ndef test_paged_deepseek(seq_len, page_size, atol=0.05):\r\n    \"\"\"Compare paged vs non-paged attention for DeepSeek (192, 128) shape.\"\"\"\r\n    device = \"cuda\"\r\n    dtype = torch.bfloat16\r\n    num_heads, num_kv_heads = 16, 16\r\n    head_dim, head_dim_v = 192, 128\r\n    scale = head_dim ** -0.5\r\n\r\n    torch.manual_seed(42)\r\n    q = torch.randn(seq_len, num_heads, head_dim, device=device, dtype=dtype)\r\n    k = torch.randn(seq_len, num_kv_heads, head_dim, device=device, dtype=dtype)\r\n    v = torch.randn(seq_len, num_kv_heads, head_dim_v, device=device, dtype=dtype)\r\n    cu = torch.tensor([0, seq_len], dtype=torch.int32, device=device)\r\n\r\n    # Reference: non-paged varlen (correct)\r\n    ref, _ = flash_attn_varlen_func(\r\n        q=q, k=k, v=v,\r\n        cu_seqlens_q=cu, cu_seqlens_k=cu,\r\n        max_seqlen_q=seq_len, max_seqlen_k=seq_len,\r\n        softmax_scale=scale, causal=True,\r\n    )\r\n\r\n    # Paged\r\n    num_pages = (seq_len + page_size - 1) // page_size\r\n    kc = torch.zeros(num_pages, page_size, num_kv_heads, head_dim, device=device, dtype=dtype)\r\n    vc = torch.zeros(num_pages, page_size, num_kv_heads, head_dim_v, device=device, dtype=dtype)\r\n    for i in range(seq_len):\r\n        kc[i // page_size, i % page_size] = k[i]\r\n        vc[i // page_size, i % page_size] = v[i]\r\n    pt = torch.arange(num_pages, dtype=torch.int32, device=device).unsqueeze(0)\r\n    cl = torch.tensor([seq_len], dtype=torch.int32, device=device)\r\n\r\n    out, _ = flash_attn_varlen_func(\r\n        q=q, k=kc, v=vc,\r\n        cu_seqlens_q=cu, cu_seqlens_k=None,\r\n        max_seqlen_q=seq_len, max_seqlen_k=None,\r\n        seqused_k=cl, page_table=pt,\r\n        softmax_scale=scale, causal=True,\r\n    )\r\n\r\n    diff = (out.float() - ref.float()).abs().max().item()\r\n    return diff\r\n\r\n\r\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\r\n    # n_block_size=128 for SM100 with DeepSeek shape.\r\n    # For causal, m_block=0 always has n_block_max=1 regardless of seq_len.\r\n    # But seq_len<=128 means 1 m_block (1 work tile), seq_len>128 means 2+ m_blocks.\r\n\r\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\r\n    print(\"Test for Bug: single work-tile (1 m_block) produces wrong results\")\r\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\r\n\r\n    print(\"\\n--- Standard (128,128) control ---\")\r\n    for sl in [64, 128, 129, 256]:\r\n        torch.manual_seed(42)\r\n        q = torch.randn(sl, 16, 128, device=\"cuda\", dtype=torch.bfloat16)\r\n        k = torch.randn(sl, 16, 128, device=\"cuda\", dtype=torch.bfloat16)\r\n        v = torch.randn(sl, 16, 128, device=\"cuda\", dtype=torch.bfloat16)\r\n        cu = torch.tensor([0, sl], dtype=torch.int32, device=\"cuda\")\r\n        ref, _ = flash_attn_varlen_func(q=q, k=k, v=v, cu_seqlens_q=cu, cu_seqlens_k=cu,\r\n                                         max_seqlen_q=sl, max_seqlen_k=sl, softmax_scale=128**-0.5, causal=True)\r\n        kc = torch.zeros(1, 256, 16, 128, device=\"cuda\", dtype=torch.bfloat16)\r\n        vc = torch.zeros(1, 256, 16, 128, device=\"cuda\", dtype=torch.bfloat16)\r\n        for i in range(sl): kc[0, i] = k[i]; vc[0, i] = v[i]\r\n        pt = torch.tensor([[0]], dtype=torch.int32, device=\"cuda\")\r\n        cl = torch.tensor([sl], dtype=torch.int32, device=\"cuda\")\r\n        out, _ = flash_attn_varlen_func(q=q, k=kc, v=vc, cu_seqlens_q=cu, cu_seqlens_k=None,\r\n                                         max_seqlen_q=sl, max_seqlen_k=None, seqused_k=cl, page_table=pt,\r\n                                         softmax_scale=128**-0.5, causal=True)\r\n        d = (out.float() - ref.float()).abs().max().item()\r\n        tag = \"PASS\" if d < 0.05 else \"FAIL\"\r\n        m_blocks = (sl + 127) // 128\r\n        print(f\"  [{tag}] seq_len={sl:>3}, m_blocks={m_blocks}: max_diff={d:.6f}\")\r\n\r\n    print(\"\\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=256 (non-TMA, 1 page) ---\")\r\n    for sl in [64, 128, 129, 256]:\r\n        d = test_paged_deepseek(sl, page_size=256)\r\n        tag = \"PASS\" if d < 0.05 else \"FAIL\"\r\n        m_blocks = (sl + 127) // 128\r\n        print(f\"  [{tag}] seq_len={sl:>3}, m_blocks={m_blocks}: max_diff={d:.6f}\")\r\n\r\n    print(\"\\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=16 (non-TMA, multi page) ---\")\r\n    for sl in [64, 128, 129, 256]:\r\n        d = test_paged_deepseek(sl, page_size=16)\r\n        tag = \"PASS\" if d < 0.05 else \"FAIL\"\r\n        m_blocks = (sl + 127) // 128\r\n        print(f\"  [{tag}] seq_len={sl:>3}, m_blocks={m_blocks}: max_diff={d:.6f}\")\r\n\r\n    print(\"\\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=128 (TMA paged) ---\")\r\n    for sl in [64, 128, 129, 256]:\r\n        d = test_paged_deepseek(sl, page_size=128)\r\n        tag = \"PASS\" if d < 0.05 else \"FAIL\"\r\n        m_blocks = (sl + 127) // 128\r\n        print(f\"  [{tag}] seq_len={sl:>3}, m_blocks={m_blocks}: max_diff={d:.6f}\")\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nwith this fix:\r\n```bash\r\n--- Standard (128,128) control ---\r\n  [PASS] seq_len= 64, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=128, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=129, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=256, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n\r\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=256 (non-TMA, 1 page) ---\r\n  [PASS] seq_len= 64, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=128, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=129, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=256, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n\r\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=16 (non-TMA, multi page) ---\r\n  [PASS] seq_len= 64, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=128, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=129, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=256, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n\r\n--- DeepSeek (192,128) page_size=128 (TMA paged) ---\r\n  [PASS] seq_len= 64, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=128, m_blocks=1: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=129, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n  [PASS] seq_len=256, m_blocks=2: max_diff=0.000000\r\n```",
